パッケージ com.shimizukenta.property

インタフェース StringCompution

すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
java.lang.CharSequence, java.lang.Comparable<StringGettable>, Compution<java.lang.String>, Gettable<java.lang.String>, Observable<java.lang.String>, java.io.Serializable, StringGettable, StringObservable
public interface StringCompution
extends Compution<java.lang.String>, StringGettable, StringObservable
String value compution, includes Getter, Observer.

NOT includes Setter.

This instance is built from other Property or Compution.

  • To build joined StringCompution, join(CharSequence, StringObservable...).
  • To toString(), CharSequence.toString()
  • To detect value changed, Observable.addChangeListener(ChangeListener)
  • To compute,
    • StringObservable.computeIsEmpty().
    • StringObservable.computeIsNotEmpty()
    • StringObservable.computeContains(CharSequence)
    • StringObservable.computeTrim()
    • StringObservable.computeToUpperCase()
    • StringObservable.computeToLowerCase()
    • StringObservable.computeMatches(String)
    • StringObservable.computeLength()
  • To wait until condition is true,
    • StringObservable.waitUntilIsEmpty()
    • StringObservable.waitUntilIsNotEmptyAndGet()
    • StringObservable.waitUntilEqualTo(StringObservable)
    • StringObservable.waitUntilEqualToIgnoreCase(StringObservable)
関連項目:
StringGettable, StringObservable, Compution
